This directory contains the Scorpion Virtual Machine and core scorpion library,
as well as tests.

A note about the Scorpion Virtual Machine
------------------------------------------

Some of the code in this project originated from the 
dalvik VM. The project link can be found here: https://github.com/asnowfix/android_dalvik
Most of the code was written by the original language developer 
Braxton Nunnally<braxtonnunnally@gmail.com> as well as being maintained 
by the original developer. Below is the standard header found in all source files.

